Package: iLBA
Title: Information Loss Bounded Aggregation
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jeehyun", "Hwang", email = "hwangjh@snu.ac.kr", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Dongsun", "Yoon", email = "dsyoon@umich.edu", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides tools based on the iLBA algorithm for constructing confidential frequency tables from a microdata set with hierarchical variables. Tha package is designed to support the confidential release of aggregated frequency tables defined on selected subsets of variables, while jointly controlling disclosure risk and information loss. It provides functions for generating masked finest level and aggregated frequency tables, as well as protected counts for user-specified cells.
